---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base title="About — Writings" description="A short note on who this site is for.">
  <article class="container-narrow about">
    <p class="hand kicker">about</p>
    <h1>Hi, I'm Shela.</h1>
    <p class="lede">
      This is a quiet place on the internet where I keep what I'm learning —
      about content systems, faith, health, and the long obedience of
      building a life that keeps growing.
    </p>
    <p>
      I work in content marketing for a B2B SaaS company by day, build AI-powered
      content systems by night, and try to walk faithfully with God through it all.
      Some of what's here is professional. Some of it is devotional. Some of it
      is field notes from a life in progress.
    </p>
    <p>
      Nothing here is polished. It's a journal, not a portfolio. But it's a
      journal that wants to be useful — so if you find something that helps,
      that's the whole point.
    </p>
    <p class="sig hand">— Shela</p>
  </article>
</Base>
<style>
  .about { padding: 3rem 0 5rem; }
  .kicker { font-size: 1.3rem; color: var(--accent-soft); margin: 0; }
  .lede { font-size: clamp(1.1rem, 1rem + 0.4vw, 1.3rem); color: var(--ink-soft); line-height: 1.6; margin: 1rem 0 2rem; font-style: italic; }
  .sig { font-size: 1.6rem; color: var(--accent); margin-top: 2rem; }
</style>
